===Noun===
{{ja-noun|k|hira=ちか|rom=chika}}
#[[underground]]
*地下２階
*:ちかにかい
*:chika ni kai
*:the second [[basement]]
=== Idioms ===
*地下に潜る
*:ちかにもぐる
*:''chika ni moguru''
*:go underground (as in a political movement)

